node.text:
To all of Doug The Pug’s fans, 

On this Giving Tuesday, it’s finally time to announce what we’ve been working so hard on and pouring so much love into for the past year. 

The @dougthepugfoundation is now LIVE and accepting donations! The mission of what Doug The Pug does every day is to bring joy and happiness. Through his visits with children battling cancer and other life-threatening diseases, it was only natural that Doug The Pug wanted to do more than just bring joy for a few moments. Families and children in treatment for cancer or a life-threatening illness have needs outside of medical support to maintain families, bring joy, and support for the battle they are on.

Doug the Pug Foundation was created to help sustain joys of childhood and alleviate financial burdens outside of treatment. It is also a goal of Doug’s to help pay for therapy dogs for children who need them. 

Just a small donation can go such a long way, and we are so grateful for all of your support. This is the embodiment of the Doug The Pug mission, and we can’t wait for you all to follow along on this journey. 

Follow our new Instagram @dougthepugfoundation to see firsthand how your donations will be helping so many children. 

DONATE at www.dougthepugfoundation.org, link in bio. 

THANK YOU!!! 

-Doug and his family 

*Special thank you to our friends for being in this video….@barbaracorcoran, @robertirwinphotography, @bindisueirwin, @jvn, @emilyhampshire, @Kaitlynbristowe, @jasontartick, @juliamichaels, @cassadeepope, @maxmusic, @hayley.leblanc, @russelldickerson 💛

node.text:
Because dogs deserve more songs about them. 🐾

Thank u for all the incredible submissions to make this video possible! It was so hard to choose but all dogs are winners here. I hope this is a song u want to sing to ur dog, please make videos doing that and tag us for a chance to get reposted! Also let me know in the comments if the song made u cry 🥺

Stream “Song For My Dog” on Spotify and iTunes!

node.text:
“When u have a National TV appearance in the morning” -Doug
•
Guess what??? Tomorrow morning, 7/21 I will be on @qvc to sell my soft, cuddly and one of a kind plushies! This is a dream come true for this little pug. I hope all my fans can tune in and support, my human is pretty nervous 🥺 Please tune-in tomorrow morning on @qvc at 9AM EST & leave a comment below if you’re going to watch and call in for a plushie! Now everyone can snuggle with me!!
